Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.39,0:00:25.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よく飽きねーな、朝からずっと匂い嗅ぎまくってさ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.19,0:00:33.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,い…いい加減に！しろよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.24,0:00:37.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,う…ててててて…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.45,0:00:41.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あれ…？おかしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.39,0:00:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you get bored? \NYou've been sniffing stuff all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.19,0:00:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.24,0:00:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.45,0:00:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I feel dizzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:01:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Party is over
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.97,0:01:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still wanna dance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.69,0:01:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.07,0:01:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, one day my passion's fire will
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.95,0:01:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,From the beginning I knew
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.70,0:01:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,One day the flames would die out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.33,0:01:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I thought I didn't need anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.25,0:01:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But even now, I'm so serious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.84,0:01:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I still have time to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.47,0:01:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... but I'm gonna burn it up, baby
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.51,0:01:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling, it's not that easy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.31,0:01:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But surely it's not that bad either
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.73,0:01:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me fire
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Light it up, baby.  \N I'm gonna burn it up, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Party is over
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling Hurry up  \N Ah... I still have time to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.09,0:02:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling Hurry up  \N Ah... I still have time to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.01,0:02:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me fire
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.85,0:02:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Light it up, baby.  \N I'm gonna burn it up, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.02,0:02:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,#9 The story of the mercilessness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:03:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo, body, hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.97,0:03:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sick, huh? Sorry, but I'm just a farmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.97,0:03:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I ain't got no medicine. \NDon't know how to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.29,0:03:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, you just sleep some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:04:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a temple. \NYour friend brought you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No! He'll leave me behind again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, he just went \Nto go fetch some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody is going to leave you behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate Manjushage, the red spider lilies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They remind me of my papa and mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Were they such terrible parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa and Mama were strong and kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.51,0:05:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, take me with you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.84,0:05:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If your mama says okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Those samurai had it coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.93,0:05:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All shivering pale like they saw a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We wouldn't even lose to Daigo's army now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Who should we get next?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on to Mama now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo, I'll play with you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph, no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go with Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I can beat up the bad guys, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get a little bigger, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.14,0:05:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna go now! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to hang you up \Non a tree again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.91,0:06:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the puffed cheeks? \NTrying to be a squirrel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no squirrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Throwing rocks. I can't use a sword, \Nso I'll beat the bad guys like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the way you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know Dororo, you can't live \Non just strength from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.14,0:06:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The samurai are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo, you hide over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-Boss! \N-Came for revenge, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.86,0:06:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay for what you did, you crooks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We only strike samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take us for some lowlife scumbags!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.29,0:07:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-Dororo! \N-Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:07:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.39,0:08:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. \NYour papa will always be your papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll round up some men and regroup.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't run away now, \Nfor the sake of the men we lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ojiya, we'll have to move around \Nfor a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,During these days, brigands  \N scourged the lands of every region.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.59,0:08:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Their brutality brought fear  \N into the hearts of the helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Samurai who'd lost their lords  \N formed their own bands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And the poor joined them  \N in order to make a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Each had their own reasons for joining.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hibukuro's band consisted of farmers,  \N and they only assaulted samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They were quite a rare band of brigands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.99,0:09:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.95,0:09:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you go beat up the samurai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's to teach them a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So that they'll treat us right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Samurai don't even get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.93,0:09:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say they've learned their lesson now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look around. \NYou've built up a pretty tough band.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you look towards the future now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you play your cards right, \Nthe lord will give you a good position.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi, have you forgotten \Nwhat they've done to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of the wars \Nthose lords started up,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,our families were killed \Nlike they were nothing but bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They burned down our village \Nthat we built up together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I've forgotten those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:10:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't hold on to things that've passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.72,0:10:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta join forces with the samurai \Nfrom here onwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.81,0:10:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a disgrace!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.73,0:10:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Say that one more time \Nand you'll get a mouthful of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.12,0:10:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The Yanagimoto guys are worn out \Nfrom fighting Daigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's our chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-No! \N-Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ojiya, Dororo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain yourself, Itachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole place is going to be \Na battlefield in no time, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the age of the samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't make a living \Nbeing stubborn like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking your men with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You coward...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.24,0:11:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tear you to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.91,0:11:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even stand on those legs now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.96,0:11:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad you can't tear me to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.59,0:12:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The flames of Hibukuro have gone out, \Nand he's just a sack of rags now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.55,0:12:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's find something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this what hell is like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, \Nbut it might not be as bad as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are Manjushage the color of blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They might've soaked up the blood \Nof those who died in war.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that. You're scaring the poor child.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Have mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It took years for us \Nto build this village up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence! We must not have any obstacles \Nin the way of our army.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,These are our lord's orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:14:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How are we supposed to live on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hands off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.38,0:14:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The lords and samurai think they can \Ndo anything if it's for a war. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.11,0:14:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget that huge pole sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Our homes were raided by brigands, \Nand my friends were all killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never understand \Nwhy I alone was left to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hibukuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how you use a spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.81,0:15:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa... Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa... Papa...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.26,0:16:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The war will end some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Once it does, \Nyou'll be able to eat all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.02,0:16:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't lose to it until then, Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be none of my business,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.21,0:16:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but samurai are giving handouts \Nover at the temple down that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.94,0:17:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.69,0:17:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I got nice and cozy with the lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.70,0:17:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but now I've gotta achieve something \Nout on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There are lots of brigands around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.75,0:17:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the quickest way \Nto gather up some men.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how's Boss doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.22,0:17:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How've you been, Dororo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.14,0:17:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking good... or maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.35,0:17:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't, Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.19,0:17:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to your mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.32,0:17:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.44,0:17:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost out. Don't got enough for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.82,0:18:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait here, Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.53,0:18:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, give me some!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.74,0:18:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You ain't got a bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but we don't got any more \Nto lend you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Then pour it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.09,0:18:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. Eat it slowly now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's yummy. Aren't you going to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, eat up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.42,0:19:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to see you like this. \NSunken down so low.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.60,0:19:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't live on strength alone \Nfrom here on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta be smart, or you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.09,0:19:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. I just need to rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.35,0:19:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.27,0:19:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, I'll go find some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.98,0:19:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here, Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The war will end some day...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.57,0:20:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't lose to it until then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.49,0:20:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama? Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.54,0:20:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't say I'm hungry anymore, \Nso please don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, Mama...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm never going to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to lose to some war...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.64,0:20:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I know not how you two are related.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.94,0:20:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But it must be difficult \Ntraveling with such a young girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I pray that Buddha will bless you \Non your journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.91,0:20:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That nun said I had the 3-day fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:20:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember anything that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.88,0:21:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for not leaving me behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. You can't see, \Nbut she washed my clothes, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,See? They don't smell anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.23,0:21:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So I had my clothes taken off?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.28,0:21:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did that nun say anything about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.79,0:21:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.41,0:21:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I know you can hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.38,0:21:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.21,0:21:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me? \NHey, I'm talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.23,0:21:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a former midwife who worked here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.89,0:22:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,who had heard that a baby without limbs \Nwas sent floating down a river.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.36,0:22:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And 3 days ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.61,0:22:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,a commander pursuing an Asakura spy \Nwas injured severely by an unknown man.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.82,0:22:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The commander said the man's arms \Nwere prosthetics.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.36,0:22:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorrow scatters in the wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.03,0:22:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,piling up to form shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.28,0:22:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Our footsteps admonish  \N indifference in such verbose ways
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.50,0:23:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,As I peek into your fathomless eyes,  \N I lose my composure
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.21,0:23:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any hope  \N in the place I am heading to?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.13,0:23:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I feign amusement and laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.34,0:23:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,because this road is so dark
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.81,0:23:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be there to shine the light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.56,0:23:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm used to playing at saying goodbye,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.94,0:23:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but I cried when I waved to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.15,0:23:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Our fiery woes fade... and fade...  \N until night falls upon us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.58,0:23:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If I knew tomorrow would be so mundane,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.91,0:23:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have said that I wanted to live
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.12,0:23:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's futile but can't help dreaming  \N of a future... a future... you are to blame
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:38.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なな…何だい？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:40.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろ…ろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:03:00.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろ…ろ。からだ…。あ…つい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.97,0:03:04.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,病か…あいにく俺は百姓だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.97,0:03:08.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,薬もねえし、どうすりゃいいかわかんねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:09.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すまねぇな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:29.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっかちゃん…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.29,0:03:33.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうかしましたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:51.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっか…ちゃん…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:54.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大丈夫。まだ眠っていなさい。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:04:01.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここは寺です。お連れの方が運んでくれたのですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:03.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:04.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:06.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いけません
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:11.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき！また…また置いてかれちまう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:16.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,安心なさい。水を汲みに行ってもらっているだけです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:21.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,誰もあなたを置いていったりしません
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:27.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,曼珠沙華は好きじゃねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:31.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お父ちゃんとおっかちゃん思い出しちまう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:36.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんなにひどい親御さんだったのですか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:38.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうじゃねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:40.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうじゃねえ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:47.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お父ちゃんもおっかちゃんも、強ぇしあったけぇんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.51,0:05:06.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お父ちゃん。次はおいらも連れてってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.84,0:05:08.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっかちゃんがいいって言ったらだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:12.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの侍ども、いいザマだったぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.93,0:05:14.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ねぇ、おかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:18.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どいつもこいつも、青瓢箪みてえなツラして震えてやがったな。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:22.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今の俺たちなら、あの大軍にだって負けやせんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:25.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちげぇねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:27.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,次はどこを狙いやしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:30.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうだな…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:33.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ほら！おっかちゃんのところに行ってろ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:35.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいら聞いてたいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:38.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろ。後で遊んでやっから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:40.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,フン、だ。べーっ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:41.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっかちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:44.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいらもおとうちゃんと行きたい！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:47.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ダメだって言ってるだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:50.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいらだって悪いやつくらいやっつけられらぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:52.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もう少しおっきくなってからだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.14,0:05:56.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,行きたいったら行きたい！行きたい！行きたい！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:59.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,言うこと聞かないと、また木に吊るすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.91,0:06:12.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どした、ほっぺた膨らまして。リスの真似か
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:14.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,フン。あんなに膨らむかい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:16.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何してんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:21.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,石投げ。おいら刀使えねえから、\Nこいつで悪い奴をやっつけて…やんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:26.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ふぅーん。そいつはいい心がけだぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:32.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だがな、どろろ。これからの世の中は、力だけじゃ生き残れねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:35.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大変だぁーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.14,0:06:38.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,侍どもが攻めてきたぞーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:41.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろ！そっちに隠れてろ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:47.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お頭！ \N-仕返しに来やがったか！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.86,0:06:50.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よくもやってくれたなこの悪党ども！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:55.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ハッ！俺たちが狙うのはお前たち侍だけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:58.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そこらの悪党と一緒にすんじゃねぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.29,0:07:02.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ぬかせー！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:25.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろ！\Nおっかちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:07:59.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっかちゃん…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.39,0:08:03.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,心配ないよ。お父ちゃんはお父ちゃんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:05.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ん、んん…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:07.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こっからどうしやす
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:10.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すぐに仲間を集めて立て直す。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:14.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここで逃げちまったら、死んだ奴らに合わす顔がねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:17.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お自夜、しばらく転々とすることになるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:19.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうだね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:34.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この時代、各地に野伏せりと呼ばれる野盗集団が存在し
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.59,0:08:38.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,力なき人々を恐れさせた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:42.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,主を失った侍たちが徒党を組む…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:46.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,貧しき者たちが生きるために身をやつすなど、
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:48.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そこに至る理由は様々
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:55.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その中にあり、農民たちが集い、かつ、侍のみを襲っていた火袋たちは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:58.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,きわめて特殊であったといえよう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.99,0:09:01.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ねえ、お父ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.95,0:09:05.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お父ちゃんたちは、どうして侍をやっつけてるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:09.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうやって奴らに教えてやってんのよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:12.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺たちも生きてる人間なんだってな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:16.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,生きてる？侍はそんなこともわかんないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.93,0:09:21.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いや…奴らも十分思い知ったんじゃないですかねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:23.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どういう意味だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:28.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,見てくださいよ。ずいぶんと腕のいい子分たちが集まった。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:32.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お頭も、そろそろ先を見たらどうなんでぃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:37.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うまく領主に取り入れさえすれば、いいご身分が手に入りやすぜ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:43.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,イタチ…あたしらが受けた仕打ちを忘れたのかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:46.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,領主たちが勝手に始めた戦のせいで、
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:50.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,親も兄弟も虫みたいに殺されて、
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:54.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,みんなで作った村も焼かれちまったんじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:57.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,フンッ！俺は忘れちまいましたねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:10:01.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,過ぎたことにいつまでもこだわってちゃいけねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.72,0:10:06.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,むしろ、これからは侍どもと手を組んで出世しなきゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.81,0:10:10.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この恥知らずが！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.73,0:10:15.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お…俺ぁ、間違っちゃいねえと思いやすがねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:21.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もう一度行ってみろ。その口にこいつをぶち込んでやる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.12,0:10:24.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わかりやしたよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:40.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,柳本のやつら、醍醐との戦で疲れ切ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:43.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やるなら今ですぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:51.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,行けぇーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:05.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんたぁーっ！\Nおっかちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:07.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お自夜！どろろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:21.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何故だ、イタチ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:29.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お頭…すぐにこの辺り一帯も、ぜーんぶ戦場になっちまう。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:31.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もう侍の時代なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:37.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これからの世の中、あんたみたいに融通が利かねぇんじゃ、\N食っていけねえんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:40.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,残った子分は俺が頂いとくぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:42.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この卑怯もんが！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.24,0:11:45.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,八つ裂きにしてやるっ…ぐわぁっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:47.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんた！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.91,0:11:51.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その足じゃあ立つのもやっとだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.96,0:11:55.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,残念だったな、八つ裂きにできなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.59,0:12:02.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,火袋の火が消えて、ズタ袋になっちまったな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.55,0:12:07.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんた！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:12.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,イタチ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:36.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,食いものを探す
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:48.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっかちゃん…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:51.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,地獄ってこんなとこかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:58.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さぁ…でも、ここよりはマシかもしれないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:21.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,曼珠沙華って、どうして血みたいな色をしてるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:26.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦で死んだ奴らの血を吸ったのかもしれねぇな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:31.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いい加減なこと言って…怖がらせないでくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:43.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やめてくれぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:48.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この村は俺たちが何年も何年もかけて、ようやくここまでになったんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:53.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,黙れぃ！我が軍が攻めいる経路にはいかなる障害もあってはならぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:55.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これは領主様の命令ぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:56.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんな！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:14:00.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,じゃあ俺たちは、これからどうやって生きていけばいいんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:02.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,離さんか！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.38,0:14:04.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さっさと焼けぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:10.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ひでえよ…こんなの…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:16.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,領主も侍も、戦を名目にすりゃ何をしてもいいと思ってるんだ。でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:19.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんたは…もうやめとくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:24.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,行くぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:27.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そこのお前、止まれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.11,0:14:34.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その大長巻、忘れようにも忘れられん。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:38.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,野党に屋敷を襲われ、仲間を全て殺された。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:44.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,自分だけが生き残ったのは何の因果かわからぬままだった。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:47.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それが今わかった！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:49.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,火袋ーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:52.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,貴様ぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:20.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,槍っていうものはな…こう使うんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.81,0:15:39.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お父ちゃん？お父ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:43.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お父ちゃん！お父ちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:46.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お父ちゃん…！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:18.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっかちゃん…おいらお腹空いたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.26,0:16:20.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦は終わる。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:23.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうすれば、お腹いっぱい食べられる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.02,0:16:27.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それまで絶対に負けちゃだめだよ。どろろ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:44.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前さん方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:45.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はい？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:49.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,余計なお世話かもしれんが、
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.21,0:16:54.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この先を登ったお寺で、お侍さんが施しをしてくださっとる。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:55.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,行ってみるといい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.94,0:17:09.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,イタチ…はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.69,0:17:15.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こいつは驚いたな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:17.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんた、何してんだい？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:21.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いやねぇ、うまく領主さんに取り入ったはいいが、
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.70,0:17:24.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今度は戦場で手柄を立てにゃあならんのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:27.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この辺りにゃ野伏が多い。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.75,0:17:31.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,必要な人手を集めるにはこうするのが手っ取り早いのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:34.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それより、お頭はどうした。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.22,0:17:38.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,…そうかい…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:40.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,久しぶりだなどろろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.14,0:17:43.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,元気そう…じゃあ、ねぇか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.35,0:17:46.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やめな！どろろ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:49.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でも…でもおいら…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.19,0:17:51.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっかちゃんの言うことが聞けないのかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.32,0:17:53.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わかったよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.44,0:17:57.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そろそろ終わりだ！全員分はねぇからな！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.82,0:18:00.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,待ってな、どろろ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.53,0:18:02.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私にもちょうだい！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.74,0:18:05.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前…椀持ってねぇじゃねぇか！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:09.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こっちが用意した分はもうなくなっちまったんだ。わりぃな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:11.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,かまわないよ！ここに！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:14.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いや…！でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:18.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,言う通りにしてやれ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.09,0:18:20.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,へっ、へい…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:42.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっかちゃん…大丈夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:46.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ああ。さ、慌てて食べるんじゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:55.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいしいよ。おっかちゃんは？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:57.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いいから全部お食べ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.42,0:19:02.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんたのそんな姿は見たくなかったぜ。落ちぶれちまいやがって
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.60,0:19:06.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:11.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これからの世の中は力だけじゃ生き残れねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:14.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここだよ、ここ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:17.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,賢くねえ奴は…死ぬぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:20.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,バッ…バカヤロー！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:38.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっかちゃん？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:41.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっかちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.09,0:19:45.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だよ…少し休めば…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.35,0:19:47.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっかちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.27,0:19:51.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,待ってて。おいら、なんか食べモン探してくる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.98,0:19:53.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいで、どろろ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:59.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,い…つか。戦…は、終わる…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.57,0:20:04.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それまで…負け…ちゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.49,0:20:07.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっかちゃん？…おっかちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.54,0:20:10.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,返事しておくれよ。おっかちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:15.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいらもう腹減ったなんて言わないから、だから死なないでよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:18.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっかちゃん…おっかちゃん！おっかちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:25.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だから、おいら…絶対、負けねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:27.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦…なんかに…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.64,0:20:32.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どのようなご関係かは存じませんが、
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.94,0:20:38.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,年端の行かぬ女の子を連れての旅はさぞかし難儀でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:44.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうかあなた方の旅路に、仏様のご慈悲がありますように。\N我建超世願…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.91,0:20:56.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの尼さんが言ってたけど、おいら、三日病みにかかってたんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:20:59.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,寺にいる間のことは全然覚えてねえや
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.88,0:21:05.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき。置いてかないでくれてありがとな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:15.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あっ！そうだ！あにきは見えねぇだろうけど、\N着物も洗ってもらったんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:18.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ほれ。臭わねぇだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.23,0:21:20.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ん？待てよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:23.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,てことは、おいら…あにきの前で服を…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.28,0:21:29.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ、あにき。あの尼さん…おいらのこと、なんか言ってた？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.79,0:21:32.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,言ってたのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.41,0:21:38.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ…あにき！おい！聞こえてんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.38,0:21:42.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんとか言え！おい、こらあにき！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.21,0:21:48.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おい、あにき聞こえてんのか？黙ってないで何とか言えよ！あにき！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.23,0:21:56.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,かつて城勤めをしていた産婆から
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.89,0:22:01.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,両腕・両足のない赤子を川に流したと聞いたものがおります
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.36,0:22:03.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さらに3日ほど前、
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.61,0:22:09.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,朝倉の密偵を追っていた国頭が何者かに襲われ、深手を負いました
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.82,0:22:15.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,国頭によれば、その者の両腕は作り物であったと…
